stories.title: New Zealand rout Pakistan
stories.summary: New Zealand upset the formbook at the Rangiri Dambulla International Stadium, snapping Pakistan's six-match post-World Cup winning streak with an emphatic seven-wicket victory - with 22.4 overs to spare - in the second low-scoring match of the
